statements: SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_activity_in_ar;

SELECT user_id, activity_type, activity_description, activity_timestamp FROM UserActivity JOIN UserARInteractions ON UserActivity.user_id = UserARInteractions.user_id WHERE interaction_type = 'like' ORDER BY activity_timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(object_id) AS total_interactions FROM UserARInteractions GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;

SELECT u.user_id, u.activity_type, o.object_name, i.interaction_type FROM UserActivity u JOIN UserARInteractions i ON u.user_id = i.user_id JOIN ARObjects o ON i.object_id = o.object_id WHERE u.activity_type = 'post' AND o.object_category = 'furniture';
